data.description: Old world meets Modern Luxury. Current owner updated home to the highest standard while preserving the charm of the early 1900's. Original hardwood floors welcome you. Central vacuum, USB ports, hand troweled walls and recessed lighting compliment the original raised panelling. Original pocket doors are preserved with their brass knobs. Porch heating comforts as the world goes by. Get pampered in the steam shower then recline by the modern fire place. Multi use zoning offers endless possibilities. If you are not in town...the very low property tax and central location may allow you to fulfill your dream of a short term rental business. A list of all improvements are provided. Just move in and a short walk later you find the  midtown shops, restaurants and the river.  Large backyard offers amenities such as an electric gate, car and  RV parking with hookups. Lockbox is located on the front door. Please use Showing Time for showing appointments. Appointment requests set to confirmed instantly ( sorry, apparently showing time experiencing difficulties)
